                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No official record of this conversation has been found. According to the account
                    in Pickersgill, p. 416, from which the information above has been derived, the
                    subject of the conversation was Canada’s desire for representation on the
                    Combined Munitions Assignment Board.</p>
